p.d: A year later, Marie finally attends her viva. An opportunity for everyone to get together, for the first time since the last events, and look back over a year spent far apart... Directed by: Stephen Cafiero (season 3, France, 2019) Screenplay: Frédéric Rosset, Camille Rosset Cast: Sébastien Chassagne (Julien), Marie Kauffmann (Marie), Théo Fernandez (Jacques), Nathalie Cerda (Sylvie), Matilda Marty (Emma), Allison Chassagne (Julie), Charlie Nelson (Louis), Amel Charif (Sam), Julie Farenc-Deramond (Léa), Martin Judas (Dylan), Bruni Makaya (Yanis) Genre: comedy drama
